	<div class="container">
		<h2>Instructions :</h2>
		<ol>
			<li>To give a line break place &lt;br&gt; instead of pressing the enter key.</li>
			<li>To hightlight some text, place it between &lt;strong&gt; and &lt;/strong&gt; for eg. <strong>highlighted</strong> </li>
			<li>To display some heading, place it between &lt;h3&gt; and &lt;/h3&gt; for eg. <h3>heading</h3></li>
			<li>To make some text italic, place it between &lt;em&gt; and &lt;/em&gt; for eg. <em>italic</em></li>
		</ol>
	</div>

